item.title: Happy to be Here
item.description: IMO Journal Man, it’s over now. Just like that a good part of what I spent my highschool life doing has come to a close. I did it, I competed at the IMO, I got an HM which is definitely not what I would’ve wanted but getting it has definitely shaped me in many ways I never imagined it would. Let me first go over what happened. Day 1 (Transit):
